title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E03 Cave of the Dead
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea
S04E03 
Cave of the Dead  

First Aired:October 8, 1967

The Seaview encounters the Flying Dutchman, who dooms the sub to roam the sea forever. Van Wyck: Warren Stevens. Crane: David Hedison. Nelson: Richard Basehart. Morton: Bob Dowdell.

My continued sharing of these rare episodes is dependent on your expressions of gratitude.
